message.content: cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.FL, cs.SE, cs.ET - This paper deals with extending the AIGER format for synthesis problems with safety specifications. The paper is likely to be categorized under Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO) as it deals with formal methods for synthesis. It may also be categorized under Programming Languages (cs.PL) as it deals with defining a format for posing synthesis problems. Additionally, it may be categorized under Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL) as it deals with defining a format for solutions of synthesis problems. It may also be categorized under Software Engineering (cs.SE) as it deals with defining a format for specifying safety requirements. Finally, it may be categorized under Emerging Technologies (cs.ET) as it deals with a new format for synthesis problems.
